Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:29.17,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,就是那样 就是那样\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}That's where I want it. That's where I want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.53,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,啊 耶 就要刷到高分了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Aw, yeah. About to hit the high score.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:34.82,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,- 耶 我们要成功了!   - 耶 帅呆了！\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}- Ah yeah， we're gonna do this! - Oh yeah, cool man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:36.38,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,真是会消磨时间啊\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Great use of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:42.62,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,而某些人则在外头暴揍克朗的脑袋\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}While somebody else is out there busting the Kraang's brains in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:44.74,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,而且不是我们\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}And that somebody wasn't us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:48.46,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,还有其他义务警员在追踪那些外星坨坨\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}We got other vigilantes out there going after those alien blobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:49.72,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我听着觉得不错\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.04,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,可以少干点活了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Less work for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.31,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,一点都不好\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}It's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:54.38,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,克朗偷走了钚\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}The Kraang stole Plutonium.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:57.07,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,而把他们干翻的人 从他们那把钚抢走了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}And whoever took 'em down stole it from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:02:57.94,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,有意思\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.88,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,也许施莱德又跟克朗作起对来了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Maybe Shredder's going after the Kraang again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:01.78,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我可不觉得那是施莱德的手下\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I don't think these were Shredder's guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:04.58,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我知道幕后黑手的确切身份\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I know exactly who's behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:07.20,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你最好别又说是佩镭射枪的松鼠\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}You better not say squirrels with lasers again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.67,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,那么我们怎么办 李奥?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}So what do we do, Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:12.82,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,要追踪那些追杀克朗的人吗?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Hunt down whoever's hunting the Kraang?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:14.95,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我想我们应该监视好这一带\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I think we better blanket the area,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:15.70,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,警惕一切\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}keep an eye out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.68,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,拉夫和凯西 继续监视胡同小巷\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Raph and Casey, stick to the alleyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:19.57,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,唐尼和麦奇 屋顶是你们的\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Donnie and Mikey, you take the rooftops.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:20.69,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,下水道我来负责\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I'll cover the sewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:22.39,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,半夜基地集合\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}We'll meet back at the lair at midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:35.98,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你觉得你这次能跟上我吗 琼斯?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}You think you can keep up this time, Jones?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:37.84,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你有什么不爽吗 拉夫?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}What is your problem, Raph?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:39.52,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,是因为消防通道的事吗?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}The whole fire escape thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:41.06,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,面对现实吧 凯西\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Face it, Casey,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:43.48,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,街头恶棍和机器忍者是一回事\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}street thugs and robo-ninjas are one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:47.95,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,但是从其他次元来的外星威胁那就是另外一个层次的了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}But alien threats from other dimensions are a whole different ball game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:50.64,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我单枪匹马地就把巨型太空虫子搞定了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I took on a giant space worm singlehandedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:53.73,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,对啊 你是单枪匹马地被它吃掉了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Yeah, you were singlehandedly eaten by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:59.12,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你跟活肠子战斗过吗?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Have you ever fought living intestines?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:00.54,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我想没有吧\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:03.66,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,底线问题 你在这件事上高估你自己了 凯西\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Bottom line, you're in over your head on this one, Casey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:04.43,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:08.30,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,也许我没受过忍者训练 但是我的帅\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I might not have ninja training, but I've achieved a level of awesome,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:11.21,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,是只有凯西琼斯能达到的程度\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}attainable only by Casey Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:12.93,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,难以言喻\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}It's mystical.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:30.82,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,哇啊 哥们 看这个 唐\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Whoa, dude. Check it out, Don.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:45.74,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你看到这个被高温烤过的碳残留了吗\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}You see this carbon scorching?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:48.37,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,他们是被某种等离子武器干掉的\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}They were taken out by plasma weapons of some sort,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:50.61,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,这个技术跟克朗的技术一样先进\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}tech that's just as advanced as the Kraangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:52.24,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我们得提醒其他人\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}We got to warn the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:58.58,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,克朗被那个不是克朗的人递给了克朗\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}The Kraang is getting their Kraangs handed to them, by those who are not Kraang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:35.05,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,不管这事是谁干的 把他们打击得相当彻底啊\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Whoever did this not only destroyed them, they obliterated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:42.93,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 不好\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:00.50,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,是克朗\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}It's the Kraang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:02.48,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,小菜一碟\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:08.34,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,等一下 头脑发热货 忍者都用潜入的\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Hold on, hothead. Ninjas use stealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:09.38,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,听说过吗\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Ever heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.49,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,刺头?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.97,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,那是你以前的宠物龟?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Is that your old pet turtle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:17.54,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,变异掉的那只?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}The one who got mutated?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:18.42,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:20.94,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,他以前是叫刺头\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}His name was Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:23.25,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,现在叫刺霸了 还记得吗?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}It's Slash now, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:26.56,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,很高兴又见到你 拉斐尔 想我吗?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Good to see you again, Raphael. Miss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:28.26,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,刺霸 你在这干嘛\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}What are you doing here, Slash?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.48,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我们在解决克朗\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}We're taking care of the Kraang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:32.22,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我现在有个新搭档了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I got a new partner now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.87,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,毁灭克朗!\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Destruction to the Kraang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.98,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,太帅了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}So awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:47.52,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,那是谁?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:49.81,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,一个叫蝾螈怪的外星疯子\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}An alien psycho called the Newtralizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:51.89,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你们在干嘛 刺霸?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}What are you guys doing, Slash?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:55.17,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,做你们这些乌龟办不到的事情 消灭克朗\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}What you Turtles couldn't: Wiping out the Kraang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.78,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,别挡道\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Keep out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:06.12,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 我来应付刺霸和蝾螈怪\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}All right, I'll take Slash and Newtralizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:07.80,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你退后点...\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}While you hang back and get...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:09.41,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,啊 凯西\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Aw, Casey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:10.96,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,贡噶啦!\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Goongala!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:13.58,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,小心!\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:19.66,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,正是我想要的东西\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Just what I was looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:24.96,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,然后是钚\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}And now the Plutonium.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:31.59,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,刺霸 我们得到要找的东西了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Slash, we have what we came for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:46.34,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,看来你也有个新伙伴了啊 拉斐尔\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}See you got a new partner too, Raphael.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.69,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,一个人类?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}A human?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:51.50,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你也会像背叛我一样背叛他吗?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}You gonna betray him the way you betrayed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:56.05,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,还对过去耿耿于怀吗 刺头?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Still holding on to the past, huh, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:59.08,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我跟你说过了 我现在叫刺霸\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I told you, it's Slash now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:17.23,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我想我们有大麻烦了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I think we're in deep trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:23.82,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我的头\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}My head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.66,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,拉夫 来点冰敷一下\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Raph, ice me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:27.94,备注,,0,0,0,,每集一卖萌的冰淇淋喵and什么都没有但什么都有的冰箱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:32.91,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你就不该参与这事 凯西\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}You should have never got involved, Casey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:35.46,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,刺霸和蝾螈怪太强大了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Slash and Newtralizer are way too powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:38.00,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,那两个呆比什么也不是 他们不过走狗屎运了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Those two goons are nothing. They lucked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.22,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,没有下次了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Won't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:40.50,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,大家专心点\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Let's focus, people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:42.29,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,现在有两个疯了的变异生物到处乱跑\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}We got two crazy mutants running around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:43.48,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,破坏大街\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Blowing up the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:45.76,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我想我们应该盯紧克朗直到他们俩出现\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I think we should shadow the Kraang until they show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:46.40,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,这个简单\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:50.42,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,既然刺霸和蝾螈怪是用钚来给他们的传送施加能量的\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Since Slash and the Newtralizer are using Plutonium to power their teleportation,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:53.01,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我们可以追踪残留的辐射痕迹\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}we can look for traces of residual radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:56.10,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,麦奇 你能别把克朗的位置吃掉吗\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Mikey, would you stop eating the Kraang locations?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:58.72,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,等一下 唐 我就要刷新高分了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Hold on, D I'm about to get the high score.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:00.43,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,就是...\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:10.85,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,有入侵者\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Intruders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:12.30,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,克朗必须提醒\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Kraang must warn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:21.22,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,行动吧\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:23.42,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,首先我们找到克朗的通讯设备\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}First we find Kraang communications.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:27.33,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,然后把这个地方炸成拉卡拉卡洛卡拉卡\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Then we blow this place to Raka Raka Roka Raka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:29.49,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,炸掉这个地方? 太危险了吧\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Blow this place? Too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.41,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,街上的人类怎么办\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}What about the humans out on the street?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:33.97,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,还记得我们相遇的那一天吗?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Remember the day we met?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:36.56,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,那个誓言?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}The vow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:02.66,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我欠你一个人情 我叫刺霸\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I owe you one. The name's Slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:06.66,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我听不懂你的话\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I can't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:14.90,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我不得不救你\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I had to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:19.30,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,他们是十个次元里最阴险的外星人\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}These are the most insidious aliens in the ten dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:21.98,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,他们把我关进牢里 他们折磨我\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}They imprisoned me. They tortured me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.80,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我发过誓 在我把他们全部消灭之前\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I have made a vow never to rest,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:27.19,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我不会停下我的脚步\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}until I annihilate all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:28.98,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我和你一起 兄弟\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I'm with you, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:33.68,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,不惜一切代价消灭克朗\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Destroy the Kraang at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:38.12,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,"不惜一切代价" 对吗 兄弟?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}"At any cost," right, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.48,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你觉得是这里吗?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}You think this is the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:53.04,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,要么就在那里\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Either that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:56.07,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,不然那里肯定在开碉堡的派对\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}or there's one bangin' party going on in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:58.57,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,快 兄弟们 我们走吧\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Come on, guys. Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:00.45,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,哇哦 哇哦 等等\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Whoa, whoa, hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:02.85,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,谁让你来参加这次盯梢的?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Who invited you on this stakeout, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:05.11,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,凯西 琼斯不请自来\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Casey Jones invited himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:13.57,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,是克朗通讯球\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}A Kraang communication orb.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:15.97,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是我要找的\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Exactly what I was looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:24.45,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,能让我也知道计划如何吗?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Want to let me in on the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:27.36,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,会的\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}In due time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.79,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,是蝾螈怪\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}It's the Newtralizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.93,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我给他起了名的\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I totally named that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:39.59,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,其实 是我起的\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Actually, I named him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:41.22,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,"其实 是我起的"\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}"Actually, I named him."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:42.73,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,快速地胖揍他一顿\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Hit 'em hard and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:45.54,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,除了你 凯西 你退后\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Except for you, Casey. You hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:07.25,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,又想挨揍了是吧 多纳泰罗?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Eager for another beatdown, Donatello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:13.10,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,离他远点!\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Leave him alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:17.33,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,凯西!\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Casey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:32.22,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你奶奶个大头鱼!\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Holy mackerel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:33.12,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,快跑!\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:01.65,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,- 你们还好吧?   - 是的 没事\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}- You guys all right? - Yeah. We're cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:04.89,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,没事? 没我你就被砸成肉酱了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Cool? You would've been flattened if it wasn't for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:06.82,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我也帮了你啊 拉夫\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I've done the same for you, Raph.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:08.46,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 是吗? 啥时候的事?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Oh, yeah? When was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:11.95,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,反正是各种时候\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Like, dozens of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:15.10,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,如果不是你拖慢进度 他们也不会跑了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}If you didn't slow us down, they would've never gotten away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:17.11,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你在搞笑么?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:19.40,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,为什么? 你觉得这是儿戏吗?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Why? You think this is a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:26.40,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你猜怎么着 拉夫? 就这样吧\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}You know what, Raph? Forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:27.28,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我走了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I'm out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:28.54,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,好极了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:30.91,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,走就是了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:32.54,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,好 我走了!\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Good. I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:34.25,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,凯西 等等 等下\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Casey, wait. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:40.29,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,怎么? 如果他耍孩子脾气 我就不需要他的帮助\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}What? If he's gonna act like a baby, I don't want his help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:41.81,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,这样不好 拉夫\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Not cool, Raph.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.59,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,人是有感情的 哥们\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}People have feelings, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.72,0:13:46.47,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,真正的 绵绵的 感情\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Real squishy feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:47.92,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,呵 我又不是人\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Well, I'm not people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:55.53,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,最好是有好事 唐尼\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}This better be good, Donnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:56.66,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我们在这上面干嘛呢?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}What are we doing up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:14:00.16,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我们要监听刺霸和蝾螈怪的所有对话\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}We are gonna listen in on everything Slash and the Newtralizer say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:07.58,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我在和刺霸摔跤的时候 我把间谍小强放在了他身上\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}While I was wrestling with Slash, I slipped a spyroach on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:10.24,备注,,0,0,0,,这个动作显然是脑补2333
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:15.38,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我们可以从龟龟phone里面听到他们所有对话\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}We'll be able to hear everything they say through my T-phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:17.18,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我懂 酷毙了 对吧?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I know, awesome, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:18.74,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我真聪明\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I'm smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:21.94,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,挺好 我还以为你只是在被揍而已\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Nice, and here I thought you were just getting beat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:25.62,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,是啊 呃 这个 我多任务操作嘛\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Yeah, well, uh, I was multitasking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:41.16,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,克朗通讯球发布了新的武器\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}The Kraang orb revealed a new weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:44.19,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,他们午夜要在码头实验\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}They're testing it on the docks at midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:51.38,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我们可以用它一举铲除克朗\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}We can use it to wipe out the Kraang once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:57.84,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,- 我们可以一起消灭整个肮脏的城市   - 还有里面每个无辜的人\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}- We can destroy this whole stinkin' city. - And every innocent human with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:14:59.09,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你是疯了吗?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:02.46,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我是来消灭克朗的 不是平民\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I'm here to take out Kraang, not people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:03.99,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我为什么要关心这个?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Why should I care?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.08,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我又不是人\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I'm not people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:07.49,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,嗯 这句话有诡异的熟悉感啊\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Hmm. Sounds oddly familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:08.97,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,如果时机到了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}If it comes down to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:11.25,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我不会冒险的 兄弟\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I won't take any chances, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:14.28,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 这下来真的了\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Okay, this just got real.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:16.84,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我们要制止它\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Let's end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:42.12,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,这是他们说的新武器吗?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Is that the new weapon they were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:47.93,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 看上去不怎么样啊\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Oh, doesn't look like much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:54.89,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,当我没说\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:04.47,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,克朗 在这\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Kraang, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:06.92,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,朝被称为这边的方向前进\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Move in the direction known as this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:08.96,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,克朗锁定目标\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Kraang targeting target.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:18.50,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的赞\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}That is what is known as awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:20.16,备注,,0,0,0,,神奇的点赞姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:25.11,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,拉卡 拉卡 洛卡 拉卡\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Raka Raka Roka Raka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.25,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,计划是这样的\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}So here's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:27.57,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你分散克朗的注意\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}You distract the Kraang,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:28.75,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我去劫持步行器\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I'll hijack the walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:31.21,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我是要信任你去操作那个机器吗?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}And I'm supposed to trust you inside that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:34.25,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我知道怎么控制 而你也别无选择\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I know how to pilot it, and you don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:41.01,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,计划是这样\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Here's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:02.58,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,刺霸 拖住克朗\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Slash, keep the Kraang busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:04.38,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我去拿下步行器\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I'm going for the walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:06.88,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,克朗 攻击一切非克朗\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Kraang, attack all non-Kraang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:08.55,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,重复 攻击\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Repeat, attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:45.33,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,克朗 小心克朗\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Kraang, watch out for Kraang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.10,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,笨克朗\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Stupid Kraang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:52.40,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,这啥都不是\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Here goes nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:25.06,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,克朗步行器被克朗劫持 劫持者为外星两栖类\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Kraang walker has been Kraang-jacked. By the alien amphibian.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:27.03,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,克朗 撤退 撤退\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Kraang, retreat, retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:41.76,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,刺头!\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:45.94,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}You.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:47.68,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你救了我 拉夫\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}You saved me, Raphael.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:53.26,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我要把你们都消灭\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I'll destroy you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:57.88,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,拉卡 拉卡 洛卡 拉卡\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Raka Raka Roka Raka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:19:00.39,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你在干什么? 打克朗的时候他们帮了我们\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}What are you doing? They helped us fight the Kraang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:02.69,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,这是我的战斗 我不需要他们\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}This is my battle. I don't need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:11.21,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,刺霸  你怎么能这样 兄弟?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Slash, how could you, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:12.98,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你不是我的兄弟\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}You're no brother of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:24.00,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,拉夫!\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Raph!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:27.73,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,接到你了 哥们\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Caught you, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:30.42,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,拉卡 拉卡 拉卡\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Raka Raka Raka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:37.84,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,拉卡 拉卡 洛卡 拉卡\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Raka Raka Roka Raka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:41.01,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,贡噶啦!\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Goongala!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:47.92,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,凯西? 你回来了?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Casey? You're back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:50.12,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我寻思等你们全部遇到麻烦的时候\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I figured I'd wait for you all to be in trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:52.46,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我再闪亮登场救你们\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}and then I'd make an awesome heroic entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.52,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,帅吧 对不?\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Pretty cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:49.49,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,耶!\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:00.09,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,嗷 帅\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Aw, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.89,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你被抵消啦 小样\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}You've been newtralized, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.89,备注,,0,0,0,,neutralize是抵消 中和的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:03.47,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 耶!\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Aw, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:04.77,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢 刺头\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Thanks, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:06.56,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,不...是刺霸\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I mean... Slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:09.94,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,你知道 我们队里总还需要一个人\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}You know, there's always room on the team for one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:12.89,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我要走自己的路 拉斐尔\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I need to go my own way, Raphael.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:16.27,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得我还是一个人好些\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Think I'm better off solo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:19.02,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,再见 兄弟\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Goodbye, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:22.45,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,将来会和大家再见的\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}I'll see you all again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:27.37,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,再见...刺头\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Goodbye...Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:29.61,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,别焦虑 拉夫\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Don't sweat it, Raph.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:32.18,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,凯西 琼斯永远在你这边\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}You still got Casey Jones on your team.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:33.99,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮 凯西\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}You did awesome, Casey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:35.95,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,是乌龟的最佳伴侣\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Best partner a turtle could have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:37.81,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,今天事太多了 大伙\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}It's been a long day, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:38.81,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,我们回家吧\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:52.75,srt字幕,,0,0,0,,拉卡 拉卡 拉卡\N{\fs28\fscy110\3c&H000000&}Raka Raka Raka.
